ewhouse communications which is owned with advance publications john s hendricks the companys founder on september   discovery holding company completed a restructuring plan discovery holdings ascent media business was spun off and the remaining businesses discovery communications llc and advancenewhouse communications were combined into a new holding company discovery communications inc the new fully public company and trades on the nasdaq stock market under the symbols disca discb and disck sec filings are submitted by the discovery holding company in may  the company announced a special dividend of shares of the companys series c common stock payable to holders of record of the companys series a common stock series b common stock and series c common stock as of the close of business on july   as a result of the dividend each holder of a share of the companys series a common stock series b common stock or series c common stock will receive one additional share of the companys series c common stock on or about august   through group nine media discovery connects with millennial audiences through digitalfirst brands nowthis thrillist the dodo source fed studios and seeker which has  billion streams per month in may  discovery and liberty global announced an agreement to form a  joint venture to acquire allmedia a producer and distributor of tv programming liberty global and discovery communications paid approximately  million for a  stake in lions gate entertainment group in november  liberty ceo mike fries joined the lions gate board of directors as part of the acquisition divisionsedit dci operates its businesses in the following groups discovery networks us discovery networks international discovery studios group discovery digital media and discovery education discovery networks usedit the companys namesake and flagship brand discovery channel first launched on june   in  discovery channels owners acquired the learning channel in october  discovery launched sever