 internship programs discovery communications provides students with various paid learning opportunities to experience firsthand what it is like to work for the leader in global entertainment students gain valuable industry knowledge through shadowing networking opportunities and handson training discovery’s internship programs serve as a vital source for building a qualified candidate pool for permanent positions search all of our open internship opportunities united states what could be cooler than interning at the home of shark week the place where the cake boss creates his masterpieces or where you can see the world’s cutest puppies playing “ruff” during puppy bowl through the discovery internship program interns have the unique opportunity to learn about the entertainment and media industry from the leader in global entertainment through a paid  week internship we hire curious creative passionate individuals across many of our offices in the united states discovery interns will be presented with exclusive handson learning experiences mentorship executive speakers and networking sessions interns will also have the opportunity to learn about discovery’s mission values culture and commitment to quality programming products and services in turn interns will be able to showcase their unique talents cultivate their skills and most importantly have fun while doing it discovery interns are natural curiosity seekers who think creatively to succeed at any task put in front them they possess ambition and tenacity that makes them an outstanding and important part of the company are you curious see for yourself what it’s like to be a discoveryintern on instagram twitter and facebook discovery offers internship positions across all departments not just mediacentric majors internseeking departments include accounting  finance ad sales business  legal affairs communications  pr creative  design digital media education engineering  media technology human resources insights  research it marketing production social media talent casting tv development tv programming  scheduling for updates on the discovery internship program like our facebook page and search discoveryintern on instagram twitter and facebook for an inside look at what it’s like to intern in discovery’s collaborative creative atmosphere our interns get just a little excited for shark week no two days are alike at discovery you never know who may stop by and chat with the interns not only do you get an amazing internship experience at discovery you get some amazing friends too our interns come from colleges all over the nation our internships offer hands on experience turning internships into dream jobs discovery interns in silver spring maryland at orientation it may be a bad week to be a seal but it is always a great week to be a discovery intern in chicago tlc interns enjoying their summer at our silver spring md headquarters discovery interns can stand up to any “hairy” situation discovery interns give back at discover your impact day discovery’s annual day of global employee volunteerism all smiles in our los angeles office for this intern help to make cards for discovery’s impact day a day of global volunteerism shark week is the most wonderful week of the year in our los angeles office interns or finterns chompie jr greeted our interns at the john hendricks innovation awards celebrating employee achievement discovery interns create a community amongst each other that lasts long beyond their internship shark week and say yes to the dress collide for these interns internship faq what departments do you offer internships in discovery offers internship positions across all departments not just mediacentric majors internseeking departments include accounting  finance ad sales business  legal affairs communications  pr creative  design digital media education engineering  media technology human resources insights  research it marketing production social media talent casting tv development tv programming  scheduling where do you offer internships internships are offered in multiple offices across the us please check our open opportunities to see where we are offering positions that semester when do you offer internships discovery has internships during the spring and summer semesters we do not offer fall internships at this time where can i find more information for updates on the discovery internship program like our facebook page and search discoveryintern on instagram twitter and facebook for an inside look at what it’s like to intern in discovery’s collaborative creative atmosphere who should apply students must be a junior senior or graduate student enrolled full time at an accredited college or university to participate in our internship program proof of enrollment will be required if selected students must also have the legal right to work in the united states and have a  gpa unfortunately recent graduates are not eligible for the program when do i apply we’re live our summer  opportunities have been posted the deadline to apply is march st after that we cannot guarantee your application will be reviewed for the position for our spring semester check back in september  housing if selected for an internship you will be responsible for securing your own housing when will i hear back due to the high number of applications we receive each semester we are unable to respond to individual requests for status updates you may be contacted for an interview any time between september and december for our spring semester and february through april for our summer semester united kingdom what could be cooler than interning with the number  pay tv programmer in the world the home of eurosport and soon to be of the olympic games the creative hub for the creators of shark week the place where our cake boss creates his masterpieces and david emmanuel has all of those fabulous women saying “yes to the dress” through the discovery internship program interns have the unique opportunity to learn about the entertainment and media industry from the leader in global entertainment through a paid  week or  month internship we hire curious creative passionate individuals across many of our offices in the uk discovery interns are presented with exclusive handson learning experiences mentorship executive speaker and networking sessions you will also have the opportunity to learn about discovery’s mission values culture and commitment to quality programming products and services in turn you will be able to showcase your unique talents cultivate their skills and most importantly have fun while doing it discovery interns are natural curiosity seekers who think creatively to succeed at any task put in front them they possess ambition and tenacity that makes them an outstanding and important part of the company are you curious see for yourself what it’s like to get discovered and become a discoveryintern on instagram twitter and facebook for updates on the discovery internship program search discoveryintern on instagram twitter and facebook for an inside look at what it’s like to intern in discovery’s collaborative creative atmosphere are you in our interns  grads had the amazing opportunity to hang out marjorie kaplan president of content for discovery networks international learning the ropes of creating content  useful tips of the trade internship faq what departments do you offer internships in discovery offers internship positions across all departments not just mediacentric majors internseeking departments include accounting  finance ad sales brand partnerships business  legal affairs communications  pr creative  design digital media engineering  media technology eurosport human resources insights  research it facilities marketing production tv programming  scheduling where do you offer internships internships are offered within our chiswick park and feltham eurosport offices please check our open opportunities to see where we are offering positions within our next intake when do you offer internships all uk discovery and eurosport internships start in july each year they run for a  week or  month period from that date dependent on which opportunity you secure where can i find more information all uk discovery and eurosport internship opportunities are advertised on the related careers sites – if you visit the corporate pages and click through to our careers links you’ll find them there who should apply students in their sandwich year of university are our main source of candidates for this programme however there are certain business areas that are open to considering talented and creative individuals without a degree – so if you are curious creative passionate and feel you can add value to our business get in touch when do i apply keep an eye out for application launch in q of each year housing if selected for an internship you will be responsible for securing your own housing but we do have some information that we can send your way – in addition to connecting you with other interns who may be open to seeking housing in groups when will i hear back due to the high number of applications we receive each year we are unable to respond to individual requests for status updates you may be contacted for an interview any time between october and december for our intake in july of the following year germany the discovery germany intern program based out of the munich office is a paid learning experience targeting current university students or upcoming graduates to gain valuable industry knowledge and skills through handson training work shadowing project management and networking opportunities italy the discovery italy internship program is a paid learning experience targeting current university students or upcoming graduates to gain valuable industry knowledge and skills internships run for  months and are based in our offices in milan and rome we also have a specific internship program focused on our advertising sales team latin america coming soon discoverycommthis is sure to enhance olympic storytelling capabilities like never before httpstcodbsucmkaolympic flame to burn brighter all year round thanks to our new olympicchannel partnership in europe eurosport… httpstcomdnxylanrt eurosport olympic flame to burn brighter all year with new olympicchannel discoverycomm  eurosport partnership in europe https…way to get fierce for projectcat and help us protecttigers debramessing httpstcoesunwugyqhrt fullpicture our ceo desireegruber with marcus wainwright at ragbones event in soho last night  celebrating discoverycomm proje…thank you for helping us spread the message and protecttigers projectcat cakebossbuddy httpstconqqataqebthank you darrenkavinoky for helping us protecttigers httpstcoxbvjednkailacumings wwf thank you for the support projectcatthank you for the great support projectcat httpstcofnyhsyvzpwere so proud to be taking action 🐯🐅 httpstcoxboybdznthe tiger’s roar is fading from our planet help discoverycomm  wwf bring it back at httpstcooievllrpd… httpstcobigcxmkrt jarettsays meet nate schoemer the dog trainer and star of animal planets rescuetosuperdog which pairs shelter dogs w veterans i…rt tamronhall cant wait for the new season to start proud of my team and honored to be part of the discoveryid family countdown begi…discovery’s announces manhuntunibomber will unveil fbi’s hunt for unibomber ted kaczynski tca… httpstcomhquvradexplore the unknown with nih ‘first in human’ is heading to discovery for a  part special august  tca… httpstcozcygdeqlf hr ‘son of sam’ special will head to discoveryid this fall follow tca for more updates… httpstcogdbvzurdeadline crime season  was just announced at tca catch the new season sept  on discoveryid… httpstcocozvhmoidiscoveryid reveals ‘drew peterson an american murder mystery’ at tca watch the premiere aug … httpstcoctjxrcjvservice dogs are coming to animalplanet ‘rescue dog to super dog’ premiere 